prediction.sparql:
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK {
  wd:Q128160 wdt:P585 ?date1 .
  wd:Q191721 wdt:P585 ?date2 .
  FILTER ( ?date1 < ?date2 )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?country ( COUNT( ?language ) AS ?numLanguages ) WHERE {
  ?country wdt:P31 wd:Q6256 .
  ?country wdt:P37 ?language .
}
GROUP BY ?country
HAVING ( COUNT( ?language ) > 2 )

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?mountain WHERE {
  ?mountain wdt:P31 wd:Q8502 ; wdt:P2044 ?elevation .
  FILTER ( ?elevation < 8091 )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?elevation )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?country ( COUNT( ?cave ) AS ?caveCount ) WHERE {
  ?cave wdt:P31 wd:Q35509 .
  ?cave wdt:P17 ?country .
}
GROUP BY ?country
HAVING ( COUNT( ?cave ) > 10 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?caveCount )

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?date WHERE {
  wd:Q211 p:P463 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P463 wd:Q458 ; pq:P580 ?date .
}
